<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna tell him exactly how I feel!</font>

177
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait... What?</font>

178
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean...</font>

179
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you <i>kissed</i> him?!</font>

180
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:22,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna beat you next time!</font>

181
00:10:22,540 --> 00:10:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru.</font>

182
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, thanks for today.</font>

183
00:10:27,690 --> 00:10:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were right. I was being 
indecisive and worrying by myself.</font>

184
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with you all of a sudden?</font>

185
00:10:33,820 --> 00:10:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna go talk to Shio properly.</font>

186
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

187
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait there.</font>

188
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

189
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:48,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

190
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. As a thanks for today.</font>

191
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

192
00:10:51,340 --> 00:10:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on. I'm not a kid anymore.</font>

193
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever. Just open it.</font>

194
00:10:57,070 --> 00:10:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you being so pushy?</font>

195
00:11:00,850 --> 00:11:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Lucky you!</font>

196
00:11:02,770 --> 00:11:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, is this...</font>

197
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darn it! I'm just missing one!</font>

198
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How rare is it?!</font>

199
00:11:11,970 --> 00:11:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to collect these a long time ago...</font>

200
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:18,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe you remembered.</font>

201
00:11:18,490 --> 00:11:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course I remember.</font>

202
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what you like.</font>

203
00:11:22,330 --> 00:11:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

204
00:11:23,830 --> 00:11:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're one of my precious 
childhood friends, too, Haru.</font>

205
00:11:36,140 --> 00:11:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You idiot! 
You're supposed to tell Shio that!</font>

206
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:42,510
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#ece9ea">Shio</font></font></b></font>

207
00:11:41,140 --> 00:11:42,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Shio!</font>

208
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello? Eiyu?</font>

209
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, I...</font>

210
00:11:46,020 --> 00:11:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to tell you...</font>

211
00:11:47,060 --> 00:11:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shio! Where are you right now?</i></font>

212
00:11:48,770 --> 00:11:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I'm at school.</font>

213
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:53,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to talk to you about something!</font>

214
00:11:53,280 --> 00:11:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you meet me...</font>

215
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

216
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Shio? Hey!</font>

217
00:11:58,590 --> 00:11:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened?!</font>

218
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard a loud sound 
and the call dropped.</font>

219
00:12:02,990 --> 00:12:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My call's not going through!</font>

220
00:12:08,570 --> 00:12:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... need to go.</font>

221
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gotta go now!</font>

222
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

223
00:12:12,790 --> 00:12:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

224
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

225
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:18,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use it! You're in a hurry, right?</font>

226
00:12:21,930 --> 00:12:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful!</font>

227
00:12:24,730 --> 00:12:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, he hasn't changed at all.</font>

228
00:12:33,740 --> 00:12:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

229
00:12:35,650 --> 00:12:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait...</font>

230
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio...</font>

231
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio!</font>

232
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody came to my office today.</font>

233
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:53,840
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#362f41">Nurse's Office</font></font></b></font>

234
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay.</font>

235
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's not at school...</i></font>

236
00:12:55,610 --> 00:12:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So she was on her way back home?</i></font>

237
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shio... Where the heck are you?</i></font>

238
00:13:02,810 --> 00:13:04,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do this!</font>

239
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't leave things like this!</font>

240
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:06,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#ebedee">Shio</font></font></b></font>

241
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:06,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#a1c882">No Answer</font></font></b></font>

242
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:06,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#7db25b">No Answer</font></font></b></font>

243
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:06,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#97ca7f">Are you okay?</font></font></b></font>

244
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:06,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#8cad70">What happened?</font></font></b></font>

245
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:06,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="10"><font color="#a1c882">No Answer</font></font></b></font>

246
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:13,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez, Shio. 
You can't do anything without me.</font>

247
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, whatever!</font>

248
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No... This is my fault!</i></font>

249
00:13:19,690 --> 00:13:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who cares about a kiss?!</i></font>

250
00:13:22,630 --> 00:13:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm such an idiot.</i></font>

251
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should've told her how I really feel!</i></font>

252
00:13:28,050 --> 00:13:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To me, Shio, you're my 
precious... precious...</i></font>

253
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's not home.</i></font>

254
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it!</i></font>

255
00:13:40,010 --> 00:13:41,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should go back 
and check all the spots again...</i></font>

256
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu!</font>

257
00:13:42,850 --> 00:13:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Shio?</font>

258
00:13:45,050 --> 00:13:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu!</font>

259
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over here!</font>

260
00:13:48,890 --> 00:13:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu...</font>

261
00:13:50,430 --> 00:13:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

262
00:13:52,190 --> 00:13:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why...</font>

263
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you in my room?</font>

264
00:13:56,400 --> 00:14:00,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't answer the door, 
so I thought you were sleeping.</font>

265
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never answered your phone!</font>

266
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry! I got flustered...</font>

267
00:14:04,930 --> 00:14:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And dropped my phone on the stairs.</font>

268
00:14:09,190 --> 00:14:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously... Don't scare me like that.</font>

269
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-So, Eiyu...</font>

270
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's...</font>

271
00:14:17,790 --> 00:14:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something 
I need to talk to you about.</font>

272
00:14:20,350 --> 00:14:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

273
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thing is...</font>

274
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, go back! That's dangerous!</font>

275
00:14:25,530 --> 00:14:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About... the kiss...</font>

276
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We kissed...</font>

277
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But let's stay friends like before!</font>

278
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make me worry. You dummy.</font>

279
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry.</font>

280
00:15:19,490 --> 00:15:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be friends like before too.</font>

281
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:27,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're...</font>

282
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My precious childhood friend.</font>

283
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the first time I've ever heard you 
say something like that, Eiyu.</font>

284
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh. Jeez. Shut up! Shut up!</font>

285
00:15:42,830 --> 00:15:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, in any case...</font>

286
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad Shio's safe.</font>

287
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you keep this up, 
we'll eventually all grow apart!</i></font>

288
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:56,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll all... grow apart...</font>

289
00:16:03,930 --> 00:16:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

290
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:13,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Me too...</i></font>

291
00:16:13,580 --> 00:16:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to, too...</i></font>

292
00:16:16,710 --> 00:16:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to kiss him, too!</i></font>

293
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:25,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Up next is the first-year's running race!</i></font>

294
00:16:26,470 --> 00:16:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready...</font>

295
00:16:27,970 --> 00:16:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Set...</font>

296
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minamo-san's fast!</font>

297
00:16:33,570 --> 00:16:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's fast and bi—</font>

298
00:16:36,130 --> 00:16:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gorgeous!</font>

299
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I finally got to tell him 
what I couldn't say before.</i></font>

300
00:16:41,730 --> 00:16:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We made up!</i></font>

301
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:48,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the start of 
the best sports day ever!</font>

302
00:16:50,490 --> 00:16:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Eiyu!</font>

303
00:16:54,780 --> 00:16:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe I'll cozy up to him 
for the first time in a while!</i></font>

304
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu! Did you see that? 
I got first place!</font>

305
00:16:59,540 --> 00:16:59,910
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#f88eee">squeeze</font></b></font>

306
00:16:59,910 --> 00:17:01,540
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#f88eee">squeeze</font></b></font>

307
00:17:02,690 --> 00:17:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

308
00:17:05,590 --> 00:17:09,760
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<i><font face="Impact"><b><font color="#5576d0"><font size="40">Fwip</font></font></b></font></i></b></font>

309
00:17:05,590 --> 00:17:09,760
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<i><font face="Impact"><b><font color="#5576d0"><font size="40">Fwip</font></font></b></font></i></b></font>

310
00:17:06,040 --> 00:17:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's admirable! Impressive!</font>

311
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing, Shio!</font>

312
00:17:12,580 --> 00:17:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Huh? Th-Thanks...</font>

313
00:17:15,530 --> 00:17:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

314
00:17:16,870 --> 00:17:19,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your eyes are sparkling like crazy!</font>

315
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:22,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so pure-looking!</font>

316
00:17:22,140 --> 00:17:24,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sparkling? Oh, come on.</font>

317
00:17:24,990 --> 00:17:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always been like this.</font>

318
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess you could say that...</font>

319
00:17:30,230 --> 00:17:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had an epiphany.</font>

320
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:34,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An epiphany?</font>

321
00:17:35,050 --> 00:17:38,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sky's been this blue all this time!</font>

322
00:17:38,570 --> 00:17:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nature has always been so beautiful!</font>

323
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To make a young body 
move with energy is...</font>

324
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:47,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">such a wonderful thing!</font>

325
00:17:48,010 --> 00:17:51,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've come to realize all of this, 
thanks to all of you...</font>

326
00:17:51,010 --> 00:17:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My precious childhood friends!</font>

327
00:17:54,890 --> 00:17:56,510
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#486eaf"><font size="40">Cringe</font></font></b></font>

328
00:17:56,810 --> 00:17:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What's going on?</i></font>

329
00:18:00,260 --> 00:18:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What happened?</font>

330
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:04,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are we all here?</font>

331
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:05,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When you got to kiss him!</i></font>

332
00:18:05,900 --> 00:18:09,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio-chan, I brought some snacks for you.</font>

333
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Red Team! What do you 
want from your enemy?</font>

334
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:14,530
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font color="#e9e9e9">White Team</font></font></b></font>

335
00:18:14,530 --> 00:18:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">F-Forget about that! 
This is an emergency! It's Eiyu!</font>

336
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu's become so gross!</font>

337
00:18:22,120 --> 00:18:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

338
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sparkle! Sparkle! Sparkly shiny!</i></font>

339
00:18:25,600 --> 00:18:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck?</font>

340
00:18:27,060 --> 00:18:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ew!</font>

341
00:18:27,950 --> 00:18:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right, that's gross.</font>

342
00:18:29,690 --> 00:18:30,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?! Right?!</font>

343
00:18:30,870 --> 00:18:35,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's as if he's been released 
from all the world's suffering.</font>

344
00:18:39,050 --> 00:18:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what are you all doing over here?</font>

345
00:18:43,330 --> 00:18:44,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

346
00:18:44,190 --> 00:18:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at you, Runako, that's a nice camera.</font>

347
00:18:47,610 --> 00:18:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't we all take a picture?</font>

348
00:18:50,090 --> 00:18:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Okay.</font>

349
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:53,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako, you dummy.</font>

350
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of us childhood friends 
have to be in it together</font>

351
00:18:56,290 --> 00:18:58,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or else it's pointless!</font>

352
00:18:59,420 --> 00:19:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, smile!</font>

353
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this a family photo?!</font>

354
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what are you 
trying to pull off, Eiyu?</font>

355
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your face is making my skin crawl!</font>

356
00:19:12,170 --> 00:19:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari...</font>

357
00:19:13,840 --> 00:19:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your face when 
you're angry is so wonderful!</font>

358
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:19,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?!</font>

359
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops! Your headband is crooked.</font>

360
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh, you're so silly.</font>

361
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>G... Gr...</i></font>

362
00:19:31,220 --> 00:19:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay? Your face is turning red.</font>

363
00:19:33,570 --> 00:19:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Whatever!</font>

364
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Eiyu!</font>

365
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, Haru-kun?!</font>

366
00:19:40,370 --> 00:19:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's shock therapy!</font>

367
00:19:42,330 --> 00:19:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, wake up!</font>

368
00:19:46,370 --> 00:19:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have so much energy, Haru.</font>

369
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means you're in good health, 
and that's a wonderful thing.</font>

370
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gross!</font>

371
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's even worse now
with his face all swollen.</font>

372
00:19:55,650 --> 00:19:57,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no, what should we do?!</font>

373
00:19:57,910 --> 00:19:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

374
00:19:58,760 --> 00:20:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako?</font>

375
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squeeze!</font>

376
00:20:07,270 --> 00:20:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not so bad.</font>

377
00:20:08,430 --> 00:20:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan's so nice, and we can 
be all lovey-dovey like this.</font>

378
00:20:12,950 --> 00:20:14,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the best!</font>

379
00:20:15,390 --> 00:20:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako, you're just like a baby.</font>

380
00:20:19,460 --> 00:20:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako! You!</font>

381
00:20:22,370 --> 00:20:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-She might be right.</font>

382
00:20:27,610 --> 00:20:29,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! You're the one 
who said he was gross!</font>

383
00:20:30,340 --> 00:20:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it kind of just grew on me...</font>

384
00:20:36,010 --> 00:20:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me too, then.</font>

385
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey!</font>

386
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Then...me too.</font>

387
00:20:55,630 --> 00:20:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What the heck is happening here?!</i></font>

388
00:20:58,190 --> 00:21:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shio said she was able to make up with him...</i></font>

389
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I'm guessing Eiyu got over 
whatever was troubling him, too...</i></font>

390
00:21:06,250 --> 00:21:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But why does he look 
all refreshed like that?!</i></font>

391
00:21:14,690 --> 00:21:16,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>W-Well...</i></font>

392
00:21:17,070 --> 00:21:21,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is super gross and it makes 
things even more annoying, but...</i></font>

393
00:21:21,230 --> 00:21:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if...this turns into 
a rom-com kind of situation?</i></font>

394
00:21:26,100 --> 00:21:27,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

395
00:21:27,560 --> 00:21:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's probably enough 
snuggly time for now, huh?</font>

396
00:21:31,780 --> 00:21:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?!</i></font>

397
00:21:49,350 --> 00:21:54,770
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<b><font color="#b5bace"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10">Translator:
Timer:
Editor:
Quality Control:
Final Quality Control:</font></font></font></b></b></font>

398
00:21:49,350 --> 00:21:54,770
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<b><font color="#b5bace"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10">Sachiko Takahashi
Mariana Martinez
Gabriella Alabanza
S Bilyeu
Rei Miyasaka</font></font></font></b></b></font>

399
00:23:06,650 --> 00:23:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all so silly.</font>

400
00:23:08,530 --> 00:23:12,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're childhood friends 
and we're acting so lovey-dovey.</font>

401
00:23:12,250 --> 00:23:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

402
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're one to talk!</i></font>

403
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The four of you mean the world to me.</font>

404
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:22,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

405
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would be weird 
for childhood friends like us</font>

406
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to be in a rom-com situation, right?</font>

407
00:23:28,890 --> 00:23:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?!</i></font>

408
00:23:32,970 --> 00:23:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next is the pole-toppling game!</i></font>

409
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm up next. Gotta go.</font>

410
00:23:35,710 --> 00:23:39,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Participants, please gather 
at the starting point!</i></font>

411
00:23:39,840 --> 00:23:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey!</font>

412
00:23:41,010 --> 00:23:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

413
00:23:44,190 --> 00:23:45,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

414
00:23:45,290 --> 00:23:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Did we all just...</i></font>

415
00:23:45,360 --> 00:23:50,070
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="12"><font color="#fdffff">Episode 11</font></font></b></font></b></font>

416
00:23:45,530 --> 00:23:50,070
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#fdfdfd">Scared? Lost Something?</font></font></font></b></font>

417
00:23:45,990 --> 00:23:50,070
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#fdfdfd">Let off Steam on Sports Day? Still Won't Start a <font size="22"><font color="#10c7e6">Ro<font color="#f13d50">m-<font color="#9341b3">Co<font color="#f8a103">m</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

418
00:23:47,300 --> 00:23:49,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}get rejected?!</i></font>

